Description: Development files for the SOEM EtherCAT master library
 Simple Open EtherCAT Master (SOEM) library for Linux.
 This package is built from the upstream SOEM v2.0.0 source
 submodule and contains headers, shared library, CMake exports, and
 pkg-config metadata for amd64 or arm64 Linux systems.
